    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a rewarding project with this budget-friendly fixer-upper! This vehicle is the perfect canvas for a mechanic or a DIY enthusiast looking to roll up their sleeves and bring a car back to life. While it currently needs some significant mechanical attention and cosmetic TLC, it offers a fantastic opportunity to own a vehicle at a fraction of the cost. If you\u2019re looking for a solid foundation to build upon, this is the one for you!",
